<subSubSection id="F1E76147694CABECB0C1B38065414F01" pageId="277" pageNumber="278" type="note">
<paragraph id="A6B9BF8882FF7C4D609408E260D71368" pageId="277" pageNumber="278">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B689E1B90F623E278CAE2E9171C2D51" pageId="277" pageNumber="278">
<normalizedToken id="9D8B9175DA45096C5467B747E40EB69B" originalValue="Bänninger">Baenninger</normalizedToken>
(1938: 151) retained 
<taxonomicName id="D0B2EF3195B2BF5B5587BC40EA88F654" authorityName="LeConte" authorityYear="1845" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Scarites" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="277" pageNumber="278" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="patruelis">
<emphasis id="FDD700C44DB804D10497F3089615687C" italics="true" pageId="277" pageNumber="278">Scarites patruelis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
LeConte, 
<taxonomicName id="0406EA0ED59DC12C4766C9CBA91AD195" authorityName="LeConte" authorityYear="1852" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Scarites" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="277" pageNumber="278" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="californicus">
<emphasis id="4044257C1EECCA7ABDAD8779CE70E3AE" italics="true" pageId="277" pageNumber="278">Scarites californicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
LeConte, and 
<taxonomicName id="4BCA1B4A709F2C8FF99AF8EBEC58AE63" authorityName="Chaudoir" authorityYear="1881" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Scarites" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="277" pageNumber="278" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="texanus">
<emphasis id="BCCDAEDB8BCFE2A077E2B961F156F703" italics="true" pageId="277" pageNumber="278">Scarites texanus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Chaudoir as valid subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="FAB8D7A081113CCAB94B07FF7B1060D4" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1775" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Scarites" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="277" pageNumber="278" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subterraneus">
<emphasis id="32D9BB5411DF4858A47794BAB6347723" italics="true" pageId="277" pageNumber="278">Scarites subterraneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. All three names are listed in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName id="7588B63417944B22DE907CC0F81F3E56" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1775" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Scarites" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="277" pageNumber="278" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subterraneus">
<emphasis id="C03AE9A8930477A14ED7A3CBCA694A82" italics="true" pageId="277" pageNumber="278">Scarites subterraneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Nichols (1988a: 49).
</paragraph>
